{% if include_postgresql_plugin %}
## Database

The generated scaffold uses PostgreSQL by default.

Database session management and models live under `{{ package_name }}/infra/db/`.

Configure the connection with `APP_DB_HOST`, `APP_DB_PORT`, `APP_DB_NAME`, `APP_DB_USER`, `APP_DB_PASSWORD`, `APP_DB_DRIVER`, and `APP_DB_DRIVER_SYNC`.

By default, the runtime uses `postgresql+asyncpg` and migrations use `postgresql+psycopg2`.

Runtime database access uses SQLAlchemy `AsyncSession` only.

The dev dependency set also includes Alembic for migrations when the PostgreSQL plugin is enabled.

Migration files live under `alembic/`, and the Alembic environment reads DB settings from `{{ package_name }}.settings`.
{% endif %}

